DataElement.preferredName: Food or Food Substance Product Material Expiration Date and Time ISO21090.TS.DATE.FULL.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A substance consumed by humans and animals for nutritional purposes. EXAMPLE(S): broccoli, donuts, pet treats The date (and time), assigned by the manufacturer, on which the product should not be used.
